snippet.title: Motor Strike: Racing Rampage Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo available on:
►Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/777460/Motor_Strike_Racing_Rampage/
►Itch.io: https://arf-initiative.itch.io/motor-strike

Welcome to the craziest savage experience! Destroy your friends in this demented action racing rampage game, play alone, with the split screen or in the online mode. Enjoy +24 tracks, 14 Vehicles and 7 weapons with 6 different game modes and feed your hunger for power!
